data.description: Just seconds from Lake Canon, which is part of the southern Chain of Lakes in Winter Haven, and mere minutes from shopping, Legoland Resort, and main roads connecting you to all that central Florida has to offer, we present to you this renovated three bedroom two bathroom block home. The home features resurfaced wood floors, new tile flooring, all new ceiling fan/light fixtures, completely new kitchen with new stainless steal appliances and granite countertops, all new bathrooms, and a brand new roof and AC. Quickly grab your Realtor or call us to get access to this incredible opportunity to own a home in the Winter Haven, Florida! Happy house hunting!!
